dengan berani.

157
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:28,590
Kakak Yuchi,

158
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:30,790
kau berkata seperti itu,

159
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,710
aku sangat sedih.

160
